{"tid":587004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國為何仍是俄國軍火最大買主？俄媒：仿製質量不到位，只好繼續買","createTime":"2018-03-10T05:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T11:09:50.000Z","uid":31208,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d8c18676b72fd0d90ffb3b73ef3c32ee9112dfaf","tid":587004,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"中國繼續大量從俄羅斯採購航空發動機等武器裝備，並開始接收S-400防空飛彈。中國去年仍然是俄羅斯軍火最主要買主。但在美國加緊制裁之下，俄羅斯是否能保住世界第二大武器出口國地位引人關注。<br />\n<br />\n仿製不過關 依賴進口<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯軍方的紅星電視台說，中國大量仿製俄羅斯各種武器裝備，其中包括航空引擎，但由於質量和技術指標仍達不到要求，只好繼續從俄羅斯進口。中國採購蘇-35戰機時，最感興趣的是這種戰機的新式引擎和雷達系統。此外，中國開發的兩款第五代戰機距離標準要求也有相當差距。"},{"pid":"b3f0f492e00db2ebaec351fdcd1f8c0feb2be70b","tid":587004,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1手買國<br />\n<br />\n2手=北韓<br />\n<br />\n3手=中東非洲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae3f6fc7221568d7586f22fbcc72faaf95f0cd3","tid":587004,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:59:45.000Z","msg":"陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f08e2425e1b0d14cab68488b25ba44c116e21f","tid":587004,"uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:16:39.000Z","msg":"自煮燃發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3d12e291ce8998242ff410262de81891946a12","tid":587004,"uid":35814,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:34:45.000Z","msg":"厲害了，我的貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0f1f444498781663b17e66ede219a1c703875e","tid":587004,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"明明係俄佬乞中國買既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家交貨果d都係早幾年講好左買<br />\n同埋就算係新買貨數量都唔會多<br />\n仲有印度先係俄羅斯武器最大買家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d33d587db57b77eed81f1636ad3e292cc2c8969","tid":587004,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T07:52:51.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年美帝為左圍德國比技術俄仔 <br />\n宜家俄仔再賣比中國"},{"pid":"17644d0f7cde5e746ede01698a28dd17b2f3be86","tid":587004,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T07:53:57.000Z","msg":"契細佬養大佬好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bb1dc6a5fd2f3c5b1a358a01d2c15e6166d3ad","tid":587004,"uid":39316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T08:26:19.000Z","msg":"連奶共既香港警隊換槍都唔幫襯國貨就知咩事啦"},{"pid":"c1fdd128fb74a479450af4322cf00801871fcb24","tid":587004,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d33d587db57b77eed81f1636ad3e292cc2c8969","tid":587004,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T07:52:51.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年美帝為左圍德國比技術俄仔 <br />\n宜家俄仔再賣比中國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T08:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自煮燃發"},{"pid":"0604